{"tid":156901,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"餓撚咪入 是日午餐 大大舊鯇魚 high翻天","createTime":"2017-03-15T05:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T09:17:31.000Z","uid":56332,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc1c606ac47e3534fbba59767601fe0f4ef174c","tid":156901,"uid":56332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日放lunch 要去買蛋糕for同事生日啦<br />\n仲未諗到食乜好.係電光火石之間 時間好似靜止左<br />\n比我眼尾見間茶記有蒸鯇魚呀 我就買左後食<br />\n<br />\n一打開個盒 見到個大大舊鯇魚 係Fish in the box 唔係dick in the box呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同事問我食咩 我斯斯然答蒸鯇魚 . 有同事表示憎惡, 有同事表示驚訝 我理得佢1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為食個鯇魚既朋友都知道鯇魚好多骨, 所以我都好撚專注.<br />\n<br />\n好在我睇個晒Doctor X呀 Doctor house, 程至美上身挑晒鯇魚d骨 慢慢享受我果件大大舊既鯇魚<br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐比左張相大家睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/133455_d7531b3bda5bcf068520f82c1669e21a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F133455_d7531b3bda5bcf068520f82c1669e21a.jpg&h=7636b214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌 由於太肚餓太好食 我食完先記得影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc30d745c0d1ee3abf7e2809d07478a8268b85c6","tid":156901,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"無睇你段文字直接睇相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55afbe2874f46ef6951ecf7d7631b33b86f16c47","tid":156901,"uid":56332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無睇你段文字直接睇相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你感受到又幾好食未"},{"pid":"37ef0c5c23fe0e3db11683871ae63031a47ff7